Comment: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:14.98,Angel VoiceENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(450,450)}My heart changes, just like the scenery.
Comment: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:19.99,Angel VoiceENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(450,450)}I can't help it.
Comment: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:32.76,Angel VoiceENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(450,450)}"Where is God?" is a whimsical question.
Comment: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:37.79,Angel VoiceENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(450,450)}Don't count on it.
Comment: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:38.45,Angel VoiceENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(450,450)}If you listen closely, you can always hear it, right?
