Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:04:01.61,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Há coisas que você não pode fazer nada,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:06.14,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}por mais que tente.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:13.71,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Tudo é preto como breu, nem as estrelas eu vejo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:18.81,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}quando essas noites continuam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:24.12,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Eu percebi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.59,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}que acho que deveria fazer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:31.99,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}o que posso agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.29,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}É a minha vida selvagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:38.71,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Vamos ser descuidados,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.58,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}de alguma forma,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:51.02,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}e tudo ficará bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:56.80,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}A resposta virá,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:05:01.89,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}então vamos pular nessa onda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:18.58,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Há algumas coisas que você não pode evitar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.36,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}não importa quanto lute contra elas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:31.03,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Se eu for pego no meio da tempestade,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:35.81,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Não vou entrar em pânico, vou me acalmar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.15,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Mesmo que a situação seja a pior,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:44.65,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Depende da sua maneira de pensar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:49.35,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Ainda há uma chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:52.30,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}É meu estilo selvagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:55.92,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Vou rir e viver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:06:01.09,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Não me importo se esbarrarmos um no outro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:08.06,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Eu engolirei minhas lágrimas, oh sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:13.63,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}A sorte virá para mim
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:18.60,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}desde que eu estiver pelo caminho da luz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.75,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}É a minha vida selvagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.53,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Vamos ser descuidados,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:44.47,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}e nós seguiremos em frente
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.03,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}de alguma forma,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:51.48,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}e tudo ficará bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:56.93,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}A resposta virá,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:07:02.13,wild lifeENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.4}Então, vamos pular nessa onda.
